Align %0: The replacement label once a choice is made regarding the alignment
Alignment: The default label for the alignment dropdown
Borders: The label for the show borders checkbox
Height: The label for the height input
Iframe widget toolbar: The aria-label for the iframe widget toolbar
left: The option to align the iframe horizontally to the left
LongDesc: The label for the long description input
LongDescInfo: Infotext for the long description field
middle: The option to align the iframe horizontally in the middle
Name: The label for the name input
OK: The label for the submit button
right: The option to align the iframe horizontally to the right
Scrollbars: The label for the scrollbars checkbox
Title: The label for the title input
URL: The label for the url input
Width: The label for the width input
WidthHeightInfo: Infotext for the width and height input
